longBusinessSummary: Hop-On Inc. develops and manufactures electronic products, distributed software, and telecommunications hardware and services in the United States and China. It offers consumer and commercial electronics. The company also focuses on offering products in the areas of Android and Chrome OS-based devices, smartphones, tablets, televisions, set-top boxes, eReaders, and mobile device applications. Hop-On Inc. was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Temecula, California.
